- Comments can be embedded on a page
- User can comment anonymously
- Comments can be paginated
- When refreshing comments, can append only new ones instead of reloading all
- User can authenticate via openid
- User can authenticate via facebook connect
- User can upload an avatar
- User can create profile information
- Comment can be voted up or down
- User has karma based on comment votes
- User capabilities can be restriced by karma
- Anonymous commenting can be disabled by client
- Client has administrator users
- Administrator users can post-moderate comments
- Comments can be disabled per-document
- Authenticated user can edit/delete their own comments